        public ChordScore chordScore(double start,
                             double chordDur,
                             int count,
                             Contour contour,
                             int... roots)
        Makes a variable number of ChordSequences and outputs them in a ChordScore.
        Parameters:
        start - Start time.
        chordDur - Bar length.
        count - Number of bars.
        contour - Contour of Tenney Harmonic Index.
        roots - Root-groups involved in ChordScore, the first chord is assigned to downbeat.
        Returns:
        A new ChordScore.
